Subject: [PATCH] drm/xe/oa/uapi: Define and parse OA sync properties
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: c8507a25cebd179db935dd266a33c51bef1b1e80
